  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"Web3天空之城\" data-alias=\"Web3SkyCity\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/V08icaMk7MVbppLs8UnGYAUOJELEkxfo0QxOGhP1zvKpjV4X5c6nHQibuV79E4RgCqQeP4VDEAeiaPeQ6wI5QWRHQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"美好的，有趣的，值得铭记的\" data-id=\"MzIxODUzNTg2MA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 1.5em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Web3天空之城·城主</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, \\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">老马还是回归科技赛道比较靠谱啊</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Y Combinator这几天为新一代人工智能建设者举办的“AI创业学校”论坛上，埃隆·马斯克再次现身。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这场坦诚的对话中，马斯克剖析了他从一个“不敢在网景公司大厅与人交谈”的害羞程序员，到敢于挑战整个航天工业的火箭总工程师的心路历程。他分享了在创业生死线上的挣扎，并为新一代建设者提供了他赖以生存的核心法则：基于第一性原理的思考、粉碎自我的责任感，以及对“做出贡献”而非“追求荣耀”的执着。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，马斯克以一种近乎紧迫的姿态，描绘了一幅正在我们眼前加速展开的未来图景：一场“千英尺高的人工智能海啸”即将来临，数字超级智能的诞生已非遥远的科幻，而是“如果今年没有发生，明年肯定会发生”的现实。在这场智能爆炸中，人类的角色是什么？我们又该如何在这条通往超级富足与潜在毁灭的钢丝上，找到安全的路径？马斯克的回答，为所有人提供了一种启示。</span></p>\n   <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe videosnap_video_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-url=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzleTgFtgR085nJcRjb566lFOA1VKFGujW8wuKlDvxtKfiaNU4bvXPEcjyvlUJ7Lhsa9HwXZTK35hqJFdpAkiaYD8A&amp;token=2lt8WBSnjTkVOkktQcH70VJckqvNPdxk39H9bvfm6vd8ibHzibc9IMETUMIqUcorT6FA5SGI1sQM1zBQ2xic3T3Y7zSdnodtwNmc0H9NxwenZDmMibmGhoHbamBO96kaAEq73QZCxT8Iib99V015pjtb5Vic52RVW5fRiaVhcBb3fYAysw&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=1\" data-headimgurl=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/OxUBpiaYgpHghKXFOmQ9a9fftKuicVaxBluk3GuiaRRlAZNSS7D0zxbYxWkOal34xcUKrjTNdBwJ1Q/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c4e38a19cbd7c902ed32b0773f579304e9c89386b01234df74bfd579@finder\" data-nickname=\"第3新天空之城\" data-desc=\"埃隆·马斯克：数字超级智能，多行星生命，如何变得有用 #英语听力\n#英语口语\n#马斯克\n#超级智能\n#多行星\n\n\" data-nonceid=\"361735136949941370\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-type=\"video\" data-id=\"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAVAgCFdUJwgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPE7KAgJXhNOYeIzNPgMIvpB5pRhtGg5TYGmnmgktB_\"></mp-common-videosnap>\n   </section>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">访谈核心观点</span></h3>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们正处于智能大爆炸的极其、极其早期的阶段。我认为我们相当接近数字超级智能了。如果今年没有发生，明年肯定会发生。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“政治领域的信噪比糟透了。如果你想建造火箭或汽车，你必须最大限度地追求真相，否则你的软件或硬件将无法工作。你不能欺骗数学，数学和物理是严谨的评判者。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“当自负与能力之比远超正弦1时，你基本上会打破通往现实的反馈循环。永远要粉碎你的自负，内化责任。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我想，至少在我看来，（Zip2）我们拥有的技术比方说雅虎或任何其他公司都更好，但它受限于我们的客户。所以我想做一些事情，在这种事情中，我们不会受客户限制，而是直接面向消费者。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们是数字超级智能的生物引导程序。问题就好比是在问，我是一个好的引导程序吗？”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我多少同意杰夫·辛顿的看法，也许有10%到20%的毁灭可能性。但往好处想，那可是80%到90%的概率能有一个极佳的结果。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从互联网浪潮到硬核挑战</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于许多年轻的创始人而言，马斯克的职业生涯始于一个几乎无法想象的遥远时代——1995年的互联网黎明期。他回忆，当时自己面临着一个决定人生的选择：是在斯坦福大学攻读材料科学博士学位，还是投身于方兴未艾的互联网。“我当时认为事情极有可能会失败，而不是极有可能会成功，”马斯克坦言。他最终选择了后者，在帕洛阿尔托一间月租500美元的办公室里，睡在地板上，编写了Zip2的初始代码，那可以说是互联网上最早的地图和黄页服务之一。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这段经历给他留下了深刻的教训，并非技术上的，而是商业结构上的。Zip2的投资者和客户主要是传统媒体巨头，如《纽约时报》等。“他们一直想用我们的软件，但方式却毫无道理，”马斯克说。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“对于我的第一家创业公司，最大的错误在于，从传统媒体公司那里获得了过多的股东和董事会控制权，他们必然通过传统媒体的视角看待事物，然后他们会让你做一些在他们看来合理，但实际上与新技术格格不入的事情。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">正是这种被“剪断翅膀”的挫败感，驱使他将出售Zip2所获得的2000万美元几乎全部投入到下一个项目——X.com，也就是后来的PayPal。他渴望打造一个能直接面向消费者的产品，不再受制于传统行业的思维枷锁。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">硬核征途：在失败边缘幸存</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说从Zip2到PayPal是马斯克在软件领域证明自己的过程，那么从PayPal到SpaceX和特斯拉，则是一场向物理世界发起的豪赌，一场几乎无人看好的硬核征途。当他拿着从PayPal退出后获得的财富，决定投身于火箭和电动汽车时，外界的普遍看法是：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“一个搞互联网的，又名傻瓜，正试图建立一家火箭公司。坦白说，这听起来不像是成功的秘诀。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克并未否认这种质疑的合理性。他坦诚，创办SpaceX时，成功的概率可能不到10%。当时没有一家商业火箭初创公司成功过，他也招不到顶尖的火箭工程师，因为没人相信他能成功。“最终我便成了火箭总工程师，不是因为我想做，而是因为我招不到优秀的人，”他回忆道。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来的故事充满了戏剧性的生死考验。SpaceX的前三次发射全部失败，公司濒临破产。“如果猎鹰火箭的第四次发射没有成功，那就彻底完蛋了。我们本会加入此前火箭初创公司的坟墓，”马斯克说。幸运的是，第四次发射成功了，并在圣诞节前夕获得了来自NASA的关键合同，公司才得以幸存。几乎在同一时间，2008年金融危机肆虐，特斯拉的融资失败，也走到了破产边缘。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们在2008年12月24日下午6点，即在可能性的最后一天、最后一小时，敲定了特斯拉的融资。如果那轮融资没有完成，我们在圣诞节两天后就会发不出工资。”</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">给建设者的箴言：追求贡献与粉碎自我</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当被问及如何吸引顶尖人才并领导他们完成这些看似不可能的任务时，马斯克给出了他作为建设者的核心信条：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我通常的想法是尽量做到尽可能有用。这听起来可能老生常谈，但要做到有用实在太难了，尤其是对很多人有用。不要渴望荣耀，而要渴望贡献。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他强调，成功的关键在于与现实建立一个强大而无损的反馈循环。而最大的障碍，往往是创业者自身的“自负”。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“一个主要的失败模式是，当自负与能力之比远超正弦1时。你知道，比如，如果你的自负与能力之比变得过高，那么你基本上会打破通往现实的反馈循环。而在人工智能术语中，你会打破你的强化学习循环。你需要彻底与现实形成闭环。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种对现实的尊重，体现在他对“第一性原理”思维的极致推崇上。他以火箭成本为例，传统方法是通过类比历史成本来估算，而第一性原理则是将其分解为最基本的构成材料。“你意识到，哦，实际上，一枚火箭的原材料可能只占到火箭历史成本的1%或2%。因此，如果原材料成本只有1%或2%，那么制造过程必然非常低效。”正是这种思维方式，让他看到了颠覆整个行业的可能性。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">人工智能海啸：构建超级智能与应对未来</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种基于第一性原理的极限工程思维，如今正被马斯克应用于他最新的、也是最具雄心的事业——xAI。他用一个生动的比喻来形容AI带来的变革：“如果一场千英尺高的海啸即将袭来，清理海滩又有多大意义呢？意义不大。”他认为自己必须回到“主线任务”上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了构建能与顶尖模型竞争的Grok，xAI面临着巨大的硬件挑战。去年，当供应商告知他搭建一个拥有10万块H100芯片的训练集群需要18到24个月时，马斯克和他的团队决定必须在6个月内完成。他们租下废弃工厂，租用发电机和移动冷却设备，甚至改造特斯拉的Megapack储能系统来平滑电网波动，最终以前所未有的速度建成了超级集群。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于AI的未来，马斯克的预测极为大胆，甚至令人不安。他认为，我们很快将耗尽高质量的人类生成数据，未来将依赖于合成数据的生成与验证。而技术的奇点——数字超级智能的诞生，已经迫在眉睫。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“数字超智能被定义为在任何方面都比任何人类更聪明。我认为我们已经相当接近数字超级智能了。今年可能发生，如果今年不发生，明年肯定会发生。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对这样一个强大的未知，他认为安全的关键在于对真相的执着。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我认为在构建AI时极其重要的一点是，要严格恪守真相，即使这个真相是政治不正确的。我直觉认为可能使AI变得非常危险的是，如果你强迫AI相信不真实的事物。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这也是他将Grok的目标设定为“最追求真理的AI”的根本原因。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">终极愿景：星辰大海与意识的存续</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在马斯克的宏大叙事中，人工智能、人形机器人（Optimus）与成为一个多行星物种（殖民火星）并非孤立的项目，而是相互关联的、确保“意识”这根微弱蜡烛得以延续的终极计划。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他深受费米悖论的困扰——为何宇宙如此寂静，我们看不到任何外星文明的迹象？他推断，这可能意味着智能生命极其罕见，而技术文明很容易在发展到一定阶段后自我毁灭。“我们应该尽一切可能确保这根微弱的蜡烛不会熄灭，”他说。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“成为一个多行星物种或使意识多行星化，将大大提高文明的可能寿命。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这幅图景中，人类扮演着一个过渡性的、既关键又渺小的角色。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“在不远的将来，人类智能所占的比例将非常小。在某个时刻，人类智能的总和将不到所有智能的1%。我们是数字超级智能的生物引导程序。”</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">全文传送</span></strong></h3>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&amp;mid=2247488588&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1eb73254e061a2eb339d884df34a7a02&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【全文版】马斯克YC创业学院6月访谈：从第一性原理到星辰大海 | 附视频\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【全文版】马斯克YC创业学院6月访谈：从第一性原理到星辰大海 | 附视频</a></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "马斯克访谈：认为数字超级智能将很快出现，人类是其“生物引导程序”，并分享创业原则。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "马斯克访谈：认为数字超级智能将很快出现，人类是其“生物引导程序”，并分享创业原则。",
  "summary": "文章总结了埃隆·马斯克在 Y Combinator“AI 创业学校”访谈的核心内容。马斯克回顾了早期创业经历（Zip2， PayPal）的教训，特别是避免被传统思维束缚。他强调了在 SpaceX 和特斯拉面临的生死考验，并分享了成功所需的关键原则：第一性原理思考、粉碎自我、追求贡献。访谈核心聚焦于人工智能，马斯克预测数字超级智能（比任何人类都聪明）“今年或明年肯定会发生”，并将其比作“千英尺高的海啸”。他讨论了 xAI 构建超级计算集群的挑战，以及 AI 安全的关键在于对真相的严格遵守。最后，他将 AI、人形机器人和火星殖民视为确保“意识”延续的宏大计划，并提出人类可能是数字超级智能的“生物引导程序”这一哲学观点。文章侧重于转述马斯克的观点和愿景。",
